description: Escoria walks near a burned building with a serious expression
Edrei stands near Escoria and look at her with a worried face. Escoria seems angry
Escoria lift her look with an angry expression
A minotaur with a golden plate is standing next to a well in a burned village
A minotaur smiles and look to the front
Escoria takes a sword from her back with a furious expression
Escoria has an angry face
A minotaur is looking al a dead person
Escoria has a furious and angry face
Escoria swings her sword with fury
Escoria attacks a minotaur with a sword. The minotaurs defends himself with a shield
A minotaur charges with a shield and lifts a punch
The minotaur punches Escoria on the belly with brute force. Escoria holds a sword and look in pain
Escoria splites blood from her mouth and has a painfull expression
Escoria steps back at Edrei's side holding her sword. Edrei seems surprised and holds his wand
Edrei moves her magic wand and cast a spell
A hoof crackes the floor with a powerful impact
A minotaur with a red cape charges forward and lifts his shield
the minotaur punches Edrei at the stomach with an agry face. Edrei drops his wand and looks scared
A minotaur with a red cloack pushes away Edrei by brute force
Escoria looks impacted and worried. A line of blood is coming out her mouth
Edrei lies on the floor without moving in a painful pose
Escoria has a furious face and looks with rage
Escoria has a cloack and charges forward with a sword enraged
The minotaur takes the sword between his arm and chest and smiles. Holds a golden shield
A golden shield impacts the side of a sword and cracks it
A minotaur with a red cape and a gold armor smiles
Escoria kneels with both hands on the floor. A strong arm shows its punch
Escoria shouts in rage and flames start to twistes around her
A minotaur covers with his red cloack and fire are in front of him
Escoria breathes heavyly with a furious look
A red cape smokes in heat
A minotaur with a golden shield and armor and a red cloac is standing linfting his hand
